s message board writing but I was on the brellserillis.net and saw guild listings.  I saw Evoluxa on the list and came here.  I just wanted to thank one of your members: alluveal.  I was grouped with her the other night in city of mist.  It was myself a monk, a warrior and a cleric.  Just the four of us were doing really well when a huge train came and pretty much took out our party.  Everybody by the cleric died and if you have ever been to the mist city you know there can be some really bad trains.  I was bound just outside in emerald jungle.  I zoned through and was immediately hit by another train and killed before I could zone back.  To make things even worst when I repopped in EJ I was killed a third time by a gorilla that someone brought to the zone.  It was really unlucky and I was so frustrated that I was about to retire for good.  I was level 41 so I lost my level after those three deaths and was in hell again.  Alluveal was there and told me not to worry.  I was so mad that I told her I didn't care and that I was going to EC to give my stuff away as soon as I could find a port.  Well one wizard responded to my request for a port then after a few minutes he just left saying that the plans had changed.  I was about to log off at this point and give up and just delete everything.  I was swearing in my group and making a huge scene.  Alluveal told me to please wait and she then called a friend cleric of hers over to rez us.  She was a level 55 with an epic and he came all the way to EJ just to rez me.  She rezzed all three of my bodies and I got my level back.  Come to find that Alluveal had begged the wizard to go away and not port me and paid him for his time and trouble then had told him that I was just frustrated and to please not take me anywhere just yet.  She knew I had to be saved from myself.  The cleric told me that she tried to give her one of her items to pay for coming so far, but that she would not take it that it was her pleasure.  She said I should be lucky to have a friend like that  I have to thank her too as well.  She told me that if something like that happened again to sit in a safe spot and walk away from the computer for a few minutes, that even though the game might make you crazy, that deleting a character or something is not the way to go.  I just cannot believe that somebody would go out of there way to beg a wizard not to port me off and then beg a friend cleric to come rez somebody she didn't even know that well.  So thank you Alluveal, I know I already did thank you but I see you have posted here and you might see this.  You are a great chanter.  Most just sit there but you were doing stuff I thought was very cool with the mezzing and stuff and your roleplaying was making the group so much fun with you and the monk lizard talking about the dark elves and Freeport and stuff.  There was one time I knew we were all going to die and you moved so fast to mez the golums that I was like damn!  You spioled me and I never had to ask for Haste.  I laughed because you had this little timer you said you kept just for warriors and their haste. This also looks like a way cool guild to be in but I already have one I'm joining and I think this one is a little too fancy for me.  :o)   Thank you thank you thank you thank you and I just wanted to say that.  I'm going to post this in another place I saw too.  Thank you alluveal.  Please look me up if yo uwant to group again in Mist City.<br>
<br>
Verga level 41 SK  I do not have a picture for my name but maybe you can make me one, alluveal.  Email me at Sliver1999@zensearch.net<br>
